data.description: This home has been used as an income producing duplex, no permits are able to be located for lower unit, but property is zoned MHR and is able to be fully insured for both top and bottom units.   Located on a large corner lot with views of the sound and beach access the street, this property consists of a top and bottom unit with separate entrances, separate outdoor showers, separate mini split systems, and each unit has a 2 bed 1 bath layout.  A new roof in 2018 and new 200 sq ft top deck built in 2021.
